ent, quality, and effectiveness of its curriculum with its faculty as required by SACS-COC. Answer 2 Visit Us Hurley Administration Bldg Suite 205 1501 W. Chestnut Street Denton, TX 76201 Mail Us University of North Texas Academic Affairs Suite 205 1501 W. Chestnut Street Denton, TX 76201 Contact Us 940-565-4259 christy.crutsinger@unt.edu Technical issues? Site last updated on February 22, 2017 Disclaimer| AA/EOE/ADA| Privacy| Electronic Accessibility| State of Texas Online| Emergency Preparedness| THECB Online Resume System Student Consumer Information| UNT Compliance Hotline| Governors Committee on People with Disabilities| Texas Veterans Portal| UNT Home Site last updated on February 22, 2017 | Important Links 